page.title: 05HOME LIFE,LIFE STYLES.CHILD
page.content: I'M FELIX FREY 11 YEARS OLD AND I LIVE AT ORCHARD HOUSE IN APPLEDORE. IT HAS FOUR BEDROOMS, A KITCHEN,A DINING ROOM A LIVING ROOM AND TWO BATHROOMS. WE HAVE 1 DISHWASHER, 1 WASHING MACHINE, 1 TELEVISION AND 1 BUSINESS COMPUTER. AND 2 CARS. I GET UP AT 7.3O HAVE BREAKFAST BRANFLKES AND A CUP OF TEA. START SCHOOL AT 9.A.M. BREAK AT 1O.45 LUNCH AT 12.OO. IN AT 1.15. END SCHOOL AT 3.3O. GET HOME AND READ BOOK, CHANGE INTO HOME CLOTHES PLAY IN GARDEN,PAINT TOY SOLDIERS ETC. HAVE SUPPER, WATCH TELEVISION IF WORTH WATCHING. BED AT 9.3O OR 1O.OO. READ IN BED FOR 2O MINUTES THEN GO TO SLEEP.
